This paper is primarily focused on computer networks and their updates, which falls under the category of Network and Internet Architecture (cs.NI). Additionally, the paper discusses algorithmic techniques and optimization problems, which could also fall under Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC) and Algorithms (cs.AL). The paper also discusses consistency properties and their implications, which could fall under Systems and Control (cs.SY) and Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS).
